Package core.data.network

Class NetworkData

  • java.lang.Object
    • core.data.AData
      • core.data.network.NetworkData
  • public class NetworkData
extends AData
    This class represents the state of our network *AS DEFINED IN THE JSON* If something isn't defined in our JSON, we will return default values. This is our "interface" between the data and the models ThornSec will build.
